# .gitignore
# Excludes local secrets, tool artifacts, and workspace-only instruction files from version control.
# Connects to: .env, AGENTS.md, Go build/test outputs, Git metadata
# Created: 2026-06-28

.env
.env.*
!.env.example
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
node_modules/
.DS_Store
*.log
dist/
build/
bin/
coverage.out
.cache/
AGENTS.md
